# ─── User-uploaded content (NOT tracked) ────────────────
# Per-game frames & labels uploaded via the dashboard, and any custom
# model a user uploads locally through "Add model" — none of this
# belongs in the public repo (privacy, copyright, and repo-size
# reasons). Provide these separately (e.g. a download link in README).
data/
pretrained_models/custom/

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# The following ARE intentionally tracked (bundled with the repo
# so users can clone-and-run without downloading or training
# anything extra, and can see example results immediately):
#   - models/, utils/                     -> YOLOv5 source code
#   - pretrained_models/yolov5n.pt         -> YOLOv5n demo weight
#   - nanodet/                             -> NanoDet-Plus source + weight
#   - universal_cloak/<game>/<model>/      -> pre-trained defense pattern
#       ├── universal_noise.pt              (ready to evaluate immediately,
#       └── loss_curve.png                   no training required)
#   - result/                              -> example evaluation output
#       ├── evaluation_summary.csv/png       (small, safe to bundle)
#       ├── log/<game>/*.csv                 (small, safe to bundle)
#       └── evaluation/<game>/<model>/       (⚠️ up to ~800 images per
#           before_clean, before_bbox,        game+model combo — this
#           after_clean, after_bbox/           can get large fast, see
#                                              note below)
# These are NOT covered by any ignore rule above, so git tracks
# them by default — no explicit "!" exception needed.
#
# NOTE: only commit the specific game/model combos you actually want
# to ship (e.g. cs2, cf) — use `git add universal_cloak/cs2 result`
# rather than a blanket `git add .` if these folders also contain
# experimental/test runs you don't want published. If repo size
# becomes a problem, consider trimming result/evaluation/*/*/before_*
# and after_* down to a handful of sample images per combo instead of
# keeping all of them.
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════